### Step 3 — Dynamic Dashboard

#### [MODIFY] [dashboard.html](file:///c:/Users/niekl/OneDrive/Bureaublad/universiteit/Essentials%20of%20entrepeneurship/website/dashboard.html)

Currently hardcoded on lines 56–59:
- Avatar: `AM`
- Name: `Anna`
- Email shown statically

**Changes in the `<script>` section at the bottom of [dashboard.html](file:///c:/Users/niekl/OneDrive/Bureaublad/universiteit/Essentials%20of%20entrepeneurship/website/dashboard.html):**
- On `DOMContentLoaded`, call `Auth.currentUser()` (or `Auth.refreshSession()`)
- Populate `#dash-name` with `user.name`
- Populate `.dash-avatar` with `user.avatar`
- Populate `#dash-email` with `user.email`
- Populate the overview stats (reservations count, rentals count, eco score) from the user's `reservations.length`, `rentals.length`, etc.
- Populate the "Recent Activity" list dynamically from the user's reservations/rentals/donations arrays
- If no user session exists → redirect to [index.html](file:///c:/Users/niekl/OneDrive/Bureaublad/universiteit/Essentials%20of%20entrepeneurship/website/index.html)

